EDWIN M. WILMER v. CHARLES R. BAGNELLE. Decided November 6th, 1925.

*697The cause was submitted on brief to Bond, C. J., Patti-son, Ubneb, Adkins, Digues, Pabke, and Walsh, JJ.

Edwin M. Wilmer, for the appellant. Adkins, J.,

delivered the opinion of the Court, dismissing the appeal, appellant to pay the costs.
